These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, zinnia, begonia
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, february, march
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere to the right of the person who growszinnia##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Flower     | dahlia | zinnia    | begonia   |
| Birthday   | november  | march | february |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-2::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, ritmeester, bluemaster
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, cricket, skiing
1. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere to the right of the bluemaster-smoker##5
2. the bluemaster-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is cricket##5
3. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
4. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is skiing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |       3       |
| Cigar      | chaman   | bluemaster  | ritmeester |
| Sport   | cricket | basketball | skiing    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, snowmobile, van
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, lily, amaryllis
1. the person who growsazalea is somewhere to the right of the person who growsamaryllis##5
2. the person who growslily is somewhere to the left of the person who growsamaryllis##5
3. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
4. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |
| Transport   | snowmobile | van | trike |
| Flower           | lily    | amaryllis     | azalea |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-4::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, iris, orchid
There are 3 different favourite colors: orange, amber, apricot
1. the person who growslily is somewhere to the left of the person who growsiris##5
2. the person who likes orange is in the middle##1
3. the person who growsiris is somewhere to the right of the person who likes orange##5
4. the person who growslily is somewhere to the right of the person who likes amber##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Flower    | orchid | lily     | iris   |
| Color   | amber   | orange | apricot |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, puzzles, collecting
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, blues, hip-hop
1. the fan of blues is on the far left##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Hobby   | puzzles | filmmaking | collecting   |
| Music-Genre     | blues | hip-hop    | funk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-6::.
House: tower, colonial, futuristic
The people have 3 different jobs:  paramedic, writer, scientist
1. the futuristic house is the scientist##1
2. the paramedic is somewhere to the left of the tower house##5
3. the futuristic house is somewhere to the right of the tower house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| House         | colonial | tower | futuristic |
| Job   | paramedic   | writer   | scientist        |

