.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-7::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, magic-tricks, rock-climbing
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, july, january
1. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in november##5
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in january##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1        |     2      |         3          |
| Hobby     | filmmaking | rock-climbing    | magic-tricks |
| Birthday   | november      | january | july             |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-8::.
3 different games are played: snooker, chess, billiard
There are 3 different favourite colors: mauve, orange, yellow
1. the person playing chess is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
2. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
3. the person who likes mauve is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
4. the person who likes mauve is somewhere to the left of the person who likes orange##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Game   | billiard | chess  | snooker    |
| Color     | yellow   | mauve | orange |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-9::.
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, egyptian, malaysian
3 different games are played: poker, whist, billiard
1. the malaysian is on the right of the person playing poker##1
2. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the right of the person playing whist##5
3. the argentine is on the left of the egyptian##1
4. the person playing billiard is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |    3     |
| Nationality    | argentine       | egyptian   | malaysian |
| Game   | whist | poker | billiard  |

