.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-10::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, sailing, soccer
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, game, chaman
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left or far right##3
2. the chaman-smoker is somewhere to the right of the siglo-smoker##5
3. the siglo-smoker is between the chaman-smoker and the game-smoker##2
4. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |
| Sport           | basketball | sailing | soccer |
| Cigar   | game   | siglo      | chaman    |

