.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-12::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, june, january
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, water, coffee
1. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
2. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5
3. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##5
4. the person drinking water is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |    3    |
| Birthday        | february | june | january |
| Beverage   | water  | mirinda         | coffee   |

