2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the right of the oliveros-smoker##5
4. the old-henry-smoker is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |   3    |
| Birthday   | september          | august     | june  |
| Cigar         | oliveros | old-henry | dunhill |

