.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-15::.
City: london, berlin, new-york
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, hamster
1. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to london##5
2. the owner of the ferret is in an even position##4
3. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| City     | new-york | berlin   | london   |
| Pet   | chinchilla | ferret | hamster |

