.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-16::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, crime, time-travel
3 different pets are kept: mouse, rat, fish
1. the person watching time-travel movies is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
4. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5
5. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | crime       | time-travel |
| Pet         | mouse | fish | rat |

